  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
    GROUP : FidoNet_Internazionale
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    Area:                           Description:ĀStatus:
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Ā~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    AMIGA.EUR ....................  Conferenza AMIGA [EUR]ĀR/W/P
    PM ...........................  Conferenza PointManagerĀR/W/P
    TRAPDOOR .....................  Conferenza TRAPDOOR [ENG]            R/W/
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

    Available: 3 Area(s)
  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------



o Added new #MESSAGE in configuration file: END_LIST
  This is an example of text shown at the end of Unlinked, Available, QueryĀlist:

  #MESSAGE END_LISTS   [R] = ReadOnly area %\    [W] = Read/Write area %\Ā[P] = Available Policy



